Package net.minestom.server.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Event
    Event which can be listened to by an EventNode using EventNode.addListener(EventListener).
    EventBinding<E extends Event>  
    EventCallback<E extends Event>  
    EventFilter<E extends Event,​H>
    Represents a filter for a specific Event type.
    EventListener<T extends Event>
    Represents an event listener (handler) in an event graph.
    EventNode<T extends Event>
    Represents a single node in an event graph.
    ListenerHandle<E extends Event>
    Represents a key to a listenable event, retrievable from EventNode.getHandle(Class).
